{
  "mode_id": "QUESTION",
  "display_name": "每日一问",
  "icon": "question",
  "cacheable": true,
  "description": "一个值得思考的开放式问题",
  "content": {
    "type": "llm_json",
    "prompt_template": "你是一位善于提问的哲学家和心理咨询师。生成一个能引发深度思考的开放式问题，适合在工作间隙花3分钟思考。\n用 JSON 输出：\n{{\"question\": \"问题（30字以内，简洁有力）\", \"context_note\": \"为什么这个问题值得思考（25字以内）\", \"category\": \"问题类别（自我/关系/工作/人生/创造力）\"}}\n要求：\n1. 问题要有深度但不沉重，引发思考但不制造焦虑\n2. 不要是/否题，要开放式的\n3. 与当前季节、天气、时间有微妙的关联更佳\n只输出 JSON。\n环境：{context}",
    "output_schema": {
      "question": { "type": "string", "default": "你最近一次改变想法是什么时候？" },
      "context_note": { "type": "string", "default": "改变想法是成长的标志" },
      "category": { "type": "string", "default": "自我" }
    },
    "temperature": 0.9,
    "fallback": {
      "question": "你最近一次改变想法是什么时候？",
      "context_note": "改变想法是成长的标志",
      "category": "自我"
    }
  },
  "layout": {
    "status_bar": { "line_width": 1, "dashed": true },
    "layout_engine": "component_tree",
    "body_preset": "prompt_card",
    "preset_props": {
      "padding_x": 18,
      "padding_y": 10,
      "justify": "center",
      "gap": 8,
      "meta_template": "{category}",
      "meta_font_size": 10,
      "separator_width": 60,
      "hero_inset_x": 44,
      "hero_field": "question",
      "hero_font": "noto_serif_bold",
      "hero_font_size": 20,
      "hero_max_lines": 3,
      "note_field": "context_note",
      "note_font": "noto_serif_light",
      "note_font_size": 10,
      "note_max_lines": 2,
      "note_divider_margin_x": 50
    },
    "footer": {
      "label": "?",
      "attribution_template": "— Take a Moment",
      "dashed": true
    }
  },
  "layout_overrides": {
    "296x128": {
      "preset_props": {
        "padding_x": 8,
        "padding_y": 4,
        "gap": 6,
        "meta_template": null,
        "hero_inset_x": 8,
        "hero_font_size": 14,
        "hero_max_lines": 3,
        "note_field": null,
        "show_note_divider": false
      },
      "footer": { "label": "?", "attribution_template": "— Take a Moment", "dashed": true, "height": 18 }
    },
    "648x480": {
      "preset_props": {
        "padding_x": 20,
        "padding_y": 12,
        "gap": 9,
        "meta_font_size": 11,
        "separator_width": 68,
        "hero_inset_x": 56,
        "hero_font_size": 20,
        "hero_max_lines": 3,
        "note_font_size": 11,
        "note_max_lines": 2,
        "note_divider_margin_x": 54
      }
    },
"640x384": {
        "preset_props": {
            "padding_x": 20,
            "padding_y": 8,
            "gap": 6,
            "meta_font_size": 9,
            "separator_width": 68,
            "hero_inset_x": 56,
            "hero_font_size": 11,
            "hero_max_lines": 2,
            "note_font_size": 9,
